Title: The Lost Flame
Description:
<A tinderbox of a Hallowfall Expedition member, its return would help honor the memory of those who bravely gave their lives.>

An expedition scout might possess knowledge about this item.>
ObjectivesText: Deliver the Expedition Tinderbox to Keyrra Flamestonge at the Shadowgrove Vineyards.
RewardText:
On the Day of Shadows, Augustine panicked and broke ranks.

There were rumors he had left Hallowfall and found a way to the surface. I see he failed.
